Insider Activity


Individual




Robert L. Salomon



Mr. Robert L. Salomon, CPA, is Executive VP, Chief Financial & Accounting Officer at Beazer Homes USA, Inc., a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants, Executive Vice President at Beazer Homes Corp., Executive Vice President at Beazer Homes Texas Holdings, Inc., Executive Vice President at April Corp., Executive Vice President at Beazer Allied Companies Holdings, Inc., Executive Vice President at Beazer General Services, Inc., Executive Vice President at Beazer Homes Holdings Corp., Executive Vice President at Beazer Homes Indiana Holdings Corp., Executive Vice President at Beazer Homes Sales, Inc., Executive Vice President at Beazer Realty Corp., Executive Vice President at Beazer Realty, Inc. (NJ), Executive Vice President at Beazer Realty Los Angeles, Inc., Executive Vice President at Beazer Realty Sacramento, Inc., Executive Vice President at Beazer/Squires Realty, Inc., Executive Vice President at Homebuilders Title Services of Virginia, Inc., Executive Vice President at Homebuilders Title Services, Inc., and President & Chief Executive Officer at Beazer Mortgage Corp.
Mr. Salomon was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Treasurer by Ashton Woods.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Iowa.



